Session Affinity
This works for CLB and ALB.

user is connected to the same backend instance for all its request. Maintained by a cookie that has an expiration.
To make sure, the user doesn't lose his session data.
This may bring imbalance in the load.

cookie names:
APPLICATION BASED COOKIES: 
  custom cookie: cookie name shouldn't be AWSALB, AWSALBAPP, AWSALBTG(reserved for use by the ELB)
  application cookie: cookie name is AWSALBAPP
  
DURATION BASED COOKIES:
  generated by load balancer.
  cookie name is AWSALB for ALB, AWSELB for clb.
  
  
  
  
